OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FVariable
OL,6,Fcloud and some clear spells. Mostly
OL,7,Fdry, although a few showers reaching
OL,8,Fthe far north towards dawn. Turning
OL,9,Fchilly in some rural spots, with winds
OL,10,Fremaining light.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FMostly dry and bright start
OL,13,Fbut turning cloudier for a time as
OL,14,Fscattered showers move south, with a
OL,15,Fcooler northerly breeze developing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
